                        <span class="col-md-8 col-sm-12 col-xs-8 sidebar_txt">
                            <h6>Lorem Ipsum dummy</h6>
                            <p>Contrary to popular belief, simply random text</p>
                            <p><font>Marketed By:</font></p>
                        </span>
